    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered the <strong>Elementalist</strong> Class.</p></blockquote><p><span>You learn the ultimate <strong>Elementalist</strong> spell: <strong>Volcano</strong>.</span></p><table style=\"width:96.2791%\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:15.3584%\"></col><col style=\"width:12.9693%\"></col><col style=\"width:27.3038%\"></col><col style=\"width:44.3686%\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Volcano</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP:</strong> 40</td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target:</strong> Special</td><td style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</td></tr></tbody></table><p><span>You channel the fury of the planet into a powerful wave of fire and magma. Choose one option: one creature you can see suffers @DMG[50 fire] damage; <strong>or</strong> you choose any number of creatures you can see, and each of them suffers @DMG[30 fire] damage. These amounts increase by 5 if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or by 10 if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>.</span></p><p><span>Damage dealt by this spell ignores Resistances and Immunities.</span></p><hr /><p>Add the @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.spells.Item.BfZqKbr38FBxLtmH]{Volcano} spell to your character sheet from the <strong>Elementalist</strong> spell list.</p>",
